Package: textir
Title:  Inverse Regression for Text Analysis
Version: 2.0
Date: 
Author: Matt Taddy <taddy@chicagobooth.edu>
Depends: R (>= 2.15), distrom, gamlr, Matrix 
Suggests: MASS
Description:  Inference for text documents and associated attributes. Includes fast sparse multinomial inverse regression for phrase counts, as well as partial least squares and related tools. 
Maintainer: Matt Taddy <taddy@chicagobooth.edu>
License: GPL-3
URL: http://faculty.chicagobooth.edu/matt.taddy/index.html
